{"tid":879834,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港嚟講 親生兄弟互插算唔算亂倫?","createTime":"2018-10-28T09:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T10:13:48.000Z","uid":51346,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f4593b9d85460068efae017a8d68677be63b047d","tid":879834,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacf16191db1ca78a1d874cc4bbe873d5940c8dd","tid":879834,"uid":94923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"香港算, 台灣唔算"},{"pid":"7fba3ce4fc38f1f8d80e3080e54feec85018d32d","tid":879834,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eacf16191db1ca78a1d874cc4bbe873d5940c8dd","tid":879834,"uid":94923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"香港算, 台灣唔算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"咁姊妹磨豆腐呢"},{"pid":"7a73dd7d292144c0c606d061dd2fe7eeb0e9cbaa","tid":879834,"uid":158411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170428/s00002/1493315282019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170428%2Fs00002%2F1493315282019&d=ZlWKHdNPxtLZfwSwDXSCp9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=fa6551ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170428%2Fs00002%2F1493315282019&h=feb995d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170428/s00002/1493315282019</a><br />\n<br />\n亂倫罪源自宗教罪 同性無血緣不適用<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】根據法例，任何男子及16歲或以上女子與異性血緣近親性交，即構成亂倫罪。有法律學者指出，近親性交在中世紀的英國屬宗教罪行，時至今天被該國法律歸類為性犯罪。此外，根據法例，亂倫控罪只針對與異性近親的性行為，但不包括與同性近親或無血緣關係親屬之間的性行為。"}]}